Ayon is available for hire

Availability: Now

Permalink



Company Name: Cartify

Overview: Cartify is an online e-commerce platform that offers a wide range of products, aiming to provide a seamless and convenient shopping experience for customers. The platform caters to various demographics and interests, offering everything from electronics and fashion to home essentials and more.

Target Audience:
Age: 18-45

Demographic: Global audience

Interests: Diverse range, including tech-savvy shoppers, fashion enthusiasts, and homemakers

Brand Identity:
Personality: Trustworthy, modern, user-friendly, and reliable
Values: Convenience, variety, quality, and customer satisfaction

Design Guidelines:
Concept: A logo that signifies convenience and ease of shopping, potentially incorporating a shopping cart or an abstract representation of it.

Colors: Open to vibrant yet trustworthy colors that resonate with a wide audience.

Typography: Modern, clean, and easily readable fonts that represent professionalism and approachability.

Style: Simple and versatile design suitable for digital and print mediums. Should evoke a sense of reliability and trustworthiness.

Competitor Logos:
Examples: Amazon, eBay, Shopify
Differentiation: Strive for a distinct identity while maintaining professionalism and user-friendliness.

Deliverables:
Primary Logo (horizontal and vertical versions)
Color Palette and Usage Guidelines
Typeface Selection and Usage Guidelines
Logo Variations (for different applications)
High-resolution formats for digital and print use

Additional Notes: Cartify aims to become a go-to platform for diverse products, focusing on providing an effortless shopping experience while ensuring quality and customer satisfaction.


Feel free to customize this branding brief further according to your specific needs. Providing a detailed brief like this helps designers understand your vision clearly and create a logo that aligns perfectly with your brand identity.
